{"tid":1778450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［真實］自稱深黃前線呃手足錢 發國難財真實仆街例子（2）","createTime":"2019-12-11T03:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T09:50:32.000Z","uid":43206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"98bb0e35086a965b94ca5066077c4903f380f322","tid":1778450,"uid":43206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"姓名：池蘊航<br />\n出生日期：14-11-1998<br />\n電話號碼：63176208<br />\nIG:C6ijail<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKrYtJ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKrYtJ7.png&h=724f32e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDqROKx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDqROKx.jpg&h=8994448e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2UGrwn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2UGrwn.png&h=da01c766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n家姐姓名：池安琪<br />\n電話號碼：69002719<br />\nFb:chi chi <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3UNEdan.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3UNEdan.png&h=c3090bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老母姓名：ka wun Lee <br />\nFb: ka wun lee<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EbTThCc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEbTThCc.png&h=0fc75984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說呢個人問人借完錢買Gear之後影都冇<br />\n但又唔係比狗咬中 之後一直追一直問<br />\n但係都係潛水 之後搵下搵下<br />\n越後越多人都有比佢呃左錢<br />\n由中同到連登借得就借 利用人既同情心<br />\n金額由幾千至幾百都有 再放埋自己阿爺阿嫲上枱要兩老幫佢食左條街數<br />\n一時作故仔話full time前線<br />\n冇錢交租 一時又話地盤冇Job<br />\n總之就一直問人借一直潛水 實質上係攞左啲錢去賭外圍<br />\n仲有偷中同錢 中同叫佢幫手買野就食左落格<br />\n我希望所有手足要小心呢啲發國難財嘅打靶仔<br />\n以上為借錢買gear證據<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rmjjda0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmjjda0.jpg&h=bcc3298d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3aOLTa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3aOLTa1.jpg&h=7d4995f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyyThCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyyThCH.jpg&h=49ae6cec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GAxHVpn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGAxHVpn.jpg&h=ded42934&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fkPGrv3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfkPGrv3.jpg&h=71d4f8be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyyThCK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyyThCK.png&h=babc6311&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y0hT14q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy0hT14q.png&h=194c406a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEOThCM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEOThCM.png&h=63e53389&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWv2Vps.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWv2Vps.png&h=5b94c350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上爲親口承認攞左手足錢去賭證據及<br />\n以黃左為藉口不斷拖延時間<br />\n<br />\n希望以後各位手足捐錢定借錢比手足時都諗清諗楚<br />\n唔係話幾千蚊好大條數但係咁樣對真係要人幫嘅前線手足好唔公平發國難財嘅人同黑警完全冇分別<br />\n由於池先生過左星期一又係再潛水<br />\n同埋加上有資料要整合所以開多個po<br />\n另外因為原樓主有事忙所以我代左佢出Po<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"7751caa513ce8fd14b9c5c3e212c97efabed0fd2","tid":1778450,"uid":43206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:31:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce677e3ac644b3ae9a2e0676b7267ec044054e72","tid":1778450,"uid":249903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:33:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99fc73c332ea250ad54728cd1a049ee282cd0b72","tid":1778450,"uid":32269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:35:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cffb5c4f6d35a3b086edd7b5a18bcba0021cec48","tid":1778450,"uid":87313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:39:53.000Z","msg":"推 dnlm"},{"pid":"057c110a46019dfaab